### Obtener todos los clubes activos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/club/
Accept: application/json

### Obtener todos los clubes (incluyendo inactivos)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/club/todos
Accept: application/json

### Crear un Club
POST http://localhost:8080/api/club
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Club San Roque",
  "acronimo": "CSR",
  "direccion": "Calle Principal 123",
  "email": "info@clubmunicipal.com",
  "telefono": "+591 4 1234567",
  "redes_sociales": "@clubmunicipal",
  "personeria": true
}

### Crear otro Club
POST http://localhost:8080/api/club
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Deportivo Juventud",
  "acronimo": "DJV",
  "direccion": "Av. Secundaria 456",
  "email": "contacto@juventud.com",
  "telefono": "+591 4 9876543",
  "logo": "http://example.com/logo.png",
  "personeria": false
}

### Crear Club mínimo (solo nombre)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/club
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Club Simple"
}

### Get club por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/club/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### Get club por ID - Por body
POST http://localhost:8080/api/club/getbyId
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": 2
}

### Editar un club
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/club/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Club Deportivo Municipal Actualizado",
  "email": "newemail@clubmunicipal.com",
  "telefono": "+591 4 1111111"
}

### Editar solo dirección
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/club/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "direccion": "Nueva Dirección 789"
}

### Editar solo acrónimo
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/club/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "acronimo": "ABC"
}

### Editar solo logo
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/club/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "logo": "http://example.com/nuevo-logo.png"
}

### Eliminar logicamente un club
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/club/3
Accept: application/json

### Eliminar otro club
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/club/2
Accept: application/json